His long-time manager, Donald Randall, said in 2012 that Moore had both female and male lovers.
Entertainer Stanton Z. LaVey, a friend of Moore's, said in 2019 that Moore was "very much bisexual, if not gay", and that his Dolemite persona helped cover it up.
On October 19, 2008, Moore died in Akron, Ohio, of complications from diabetes.
